d","tid":441143,"uid":148679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T18:09:01.000Z","msg":"以前我用開幾十蚊個D泥都覺得點解要買幾百蚊一盒仔泥<br />\n之後試過貴野後返唔到轉頭<br />\n<br />\n一黎貴野佢用既成份係偏護髮成份, 假如你用埋D垃圾野衰D講第日個頭有咩事睇醫生都唔止個條數<br />\n<br />\n二黎造型效果或者陣味都香過人, 唔係幾十蚊既產品可以做到<br />\n<br />\n三黎一盒野當你日日GEL你都可以用到最少3個月<br />\n你自己除一除條數<br />\n都覺得唔值就當我無講過<br />\nbtw 你幼髮既話MM夠曬做"},{"pid":"2f48fa32b570c6e6ea892e9f0f0754cb9a5edfe7","tid":441143,"uid":35490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"用過覺得短髮既話quicksand 個效果最好, 中長度就mm"},{"pid":"3a31c978f4dce867893afeb54b0e518c266c5ef5","tid":441143,"uid":150124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:53:59.000Z","msg":"Blumaan meraki淨係打底啱用, 用黎gel頭唔hold又好快乾同埋kick到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMM就用緊chrome, 夠hold又易洗又易apply上頭, 我諗matte finish果盒應該差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nQuicksand未用過"},{"pid":"3d445a78b410bae29c76087f4357f6ad12386d97","tid":441143,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T04:58:47.000Z","msg":"淨係用過quicksand 長頭髮真係冇撚用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449a28f48bba79fa56169eb8badcb1be3052cd56","tid":441143,"uid":52102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:03:29.000Z","msg":"唔洗講一定mm 各方面都屌打另外兩隻"},{"pid":"9bbfe3053d389d85c2c47882f15e7b37ffc626df","tid":441143,"uid":17064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T15:45:03.000Z","msg":"Blumaan垃圾難洗又唔hold都吹奏"},{"pid":"9c4f5ba84b94316630d42aae483cde9d6444ec3d","tid":441143,"uid":148679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:01:42.000Z","msg":"有盒qs想放<br />\n用左冇10次仲有最少7成<br />\n有興趣試下就pm"},{"pid":"51006701dfc4d9d88fe1729b23571fcfb5ba5ed4","tid":441143,"uid":94311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:23:19.000Z","m